出派比同學宣傳📃）<br />\n<br />\n最後，教育同行全體祝大家有個Yellow Christmas 🎄💛<br />\n<br />\n*我地已盡量向店方直接確認到會服務，但始終人手有限，資料未必齊全，歡迎各位Comment報料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkteacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkteacher&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=f9597f92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkteacher</a><br />\nFb: shorturl.at/kqtJM<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstandbyeducatorshk%3Figshid%3Djuzv8s7rtxb5&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=02a2a24a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5</a>"},{"pid":"43cd6f9bd2b1425e4715a39134ed462c33ad2432","tid":1776170,"uid":152815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ad786de0e5387e481642ef95e916ad5681eed50","tid":1776170,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:44:26.000Z","msg":"Pusj"},{"pid":"d9aa7e09531320a7f4a45487e4ac703807b6a90c","tid":1776170,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:49:00.000Z","msg":"屌你次次都約出黎俾人捉，幾時先識咩叫地下活動，唔好再用TG呢啲on9嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b8aee42ed0cdfe1e0b656eed8626ff3f45811f","tid":1776170,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7cc87a7808b008e1557cffeadf4e41aabece08a","tid":1776170,"uid":57862,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"663081f71cf388ec50aedcf66024a9c2ae358506","tid":1776170,"uid":178078,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"突然臨放工時間有人提議堵路<br />\n之後比藍絲同狗合力捉到一兩個<br />\n成件事其實有啲鬼<br />\n作為大埔人都唔知有呢單野"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"收工搞有咩意義...<br />\n局黎?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:56:00.000Z","msg":"明顯